				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ee790af elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="ee790af" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>Unitedworld School of Business re-welcomed the students of semesters 3 and 5 with enthusiasm and words of wisdom for the upcoming academic year ahead!</p>
<p>The students had an interactive session with their faculty members and got to know about the university&#8217;s legal, academic and administrative policies.</p>
<p>We are excited for the students to be back and fill the campus with a storm of ideas!</p>
				</div>
